4. Dependency
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Etherwall needs dependency package, so You'll need:

  Guido van Rossum's Python >= 2.5.2
  Philippe Biondi's Scapy (Already include in etherwall)
  Arptables by Ebtables (Use version 0.0.3-4 for kernel versions 2.6.16 and above), Please check information about arptables at http://ebtables.sourceforge.net/downloads/latest.html
  James Henstridge's python GTK
  Fred N. van Kempen and Bernd Eckenfels's Arp
  Fred N. van Kempen, Alan Cox, Phil Blundell and Andi Kleen's Ifconfig
  Van Jacobson, Craig Leres and Steven McCanne's Tcpdump

5. End User
~~~~~~~~~~~

intended for the personal computer use only.


